data.description: Welcome to your new oasis at 116 Sweet Gum, a stunning 3-bedroom, 3-bath home nestled in the gated community of Woodside. This private cul-de-sac home is perched on the 3rd hole of the Jones Course, offering breathtaking views of the rolling greens and lush fairways. New siding has been installed; fresh mulch has been added to the established garden beds giving a fresh new feel to the property. ''Courtyard'' style parking allows for privacy coming and going. Upon entering the home you are met with an abundance of natural light streaming through the oversized windows. The hard wood floors and fresh paint bring warmth and coziness to the living room and formal dining room. The spacious eat-in kitchen is a chef's dream, with ample counter space, a peninsula for casual dining, and floor-to-ceiling windows that showcase the stunning golf course views. Access to the screened porch from the kitchen allows for a wonderful experience of blended in-door, outdoor entertainment. Entering from the garage there is access to a covered side porch, a ''drop zone'' / mudroom, and an oversized laundry room with a utility sink for convenience. The en suite offers dual vanities, walk-in closet, private commode, a jetted tub, separate standup shower, and sky light. There are two additional bedroom suites, one on the main level and one on the second level, which offer generous space for family and guests. This home is perfect for anyone who seeks a luxurious and private lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to call 116 Sweet Gum home. Call to schedule a tour today.
